<ns3053:section xmlns:ns3053="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" xml:id="resources.information.technologies.java.j2se.security.jaas.theLoginContext">
    
    <ns3054:title xmlns:ns3054="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">The Login Context</ns3054:title>

<ns3055:para xmlns:ns3055="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
The <ns3056:emphasis xmlns:ns3056="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">LoginContext</ns3056:emphasis> class encapsulates the generic framework used to 
authenticate subjects. It provides the interface to the pluggable
authentication technology used. A Configuration specifies the 
authentication technology, or <ns3057:emphasis xmlns:ns3057="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">LoginModule</ns3057:emphasis>, to be used with a particular 
application -- different <ns3058:emphasis xmlns:ns3058="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">LoginModule</ns3058:emphasis>s can be plugged in under an 
application without requiring any modifications to the application itself. 
</ns3055:para>
    
<ns3059:para xmlns:ns3059="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
The login module supplies the following services:
<ns3060:orderedlist xmlns:ns3060="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
   <ns3061:listitem xmlns:ns3061="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"><ns3062:formalpara xmlns:ns3062="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"><ns3063:title xmlns:ns3063="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">login()</ns3063:title> <ns3064:para xmlns:ns3064="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">performs the authentication and, if successful, 
                  associates principals and credentials with the 
                  authenticated Subject. </ns3064:para></ns3062:formalpara></ns3061:listitem>
                  
   <ns3065:listitem xmlns:ns3065="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"><ns3066:formalpara xmlns:ns3066="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"><ns3067:title xmlns:ns3067="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">getSubject()</ns3067:title><ns3068:para xmlns:ns3068="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"> returns the authenticated Subject. </ns3068:para></ns3066:formalpara></ns3065:listitem>

   <ns3069:listitem xmlns:ns3069="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"><ns3070:formalpara xmlns:ns3070="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"><ns3071:title xmlns:ns3071="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">logout()</ns3071:title><ns3072:para xmlns:ns3072="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"> logs the subject out.</ns3072:para></ns3070:formalpara></ns3069:listitem>
    </ns3060:orderedlist>
</ns3059:para>
    
